data.description: This large corner lot with mature landscaping highlights this Single-Story, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single family home. Located in the quaint community of Calimesa this home is waiting for a new owner to add some updates to its solid bones. The home features a large family room with stone fireplace, dining area, and galley kitchen with plenty of natural light. All bedrooms are spacious with ample closet space, including the master bedroom which has a lovely large bathroom. The 3rd bedroom has mirrored closet doors and sliding door access to the covered patio which is expansive with endless possibilities. Just minutes from the 10 freeway, the mountain communities of Arrowhead & Big Bear as well as the desert communities of Palm Springs & Palm Desert... all within a 1 hour drive.
